    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Lumber produced by overlaying and adhering multiple layers of thin wood. This composite wood product is stronger and more uniform than conventional milled lumber and less likely to warp or shrink.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
